data.description: Step into this spacious 3 bed 2.5 bath Townhome with a large 2 car garage. Cool-tone Tile throughout the 1st floor with Bamboo wood flooring upstairs. The home's kitchen features new Stainless Steel appliances amongst its thoughtful layout with plenty of cabinet storage, pantry and counter-space. The backyard features low-maintainance landscaping, expansive patio area is fully fenced/enclosed. This fantastic Townhome is located in a charming Henderson community near shopping, dining, recreation and the Boulder Highway redevelopment project with easy access to the 95 highway. All just minutes away from the Airport and World-Class Entertainment of the Famous Las Vegas Strip.
